      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-12-08T04:15:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don’t remember what we were thinking when we wrote this, but I think we were trying to make it so that we’d at least collect as much information as possible if we encountered some kind of failure here. This “break” makes sense to me under that rationale, because if it hits, there’s no way to progress to the succeeding element…",
      "revId": "c4df4adc9addbd534e0e90b9fcc28d362a596d53",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "b7028162_e9519ba0",
        "filename": "util/win/process_info.cc",
