        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-12-08T04:15:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "…but this one might be better as a “continue” instead.",
      "revId": "c4df4adc9addbd534e0e90b9fcc28d362a596d53",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
